maven-latex-plugin

Use the maven-latex-plugin in your Maven2 projects to automatically create pdf and/or html documents from your LaTeX sources. The plugin will call the LaTeX and TeX4Ht scripts to do the necessary work.

Homepage: http://akquinet.github.com/maven-latex-plugin

Maven2 repository: http://akquinet.github.com/maven-latex-plugin/maven2

Project on GitHub: https://github.com/akquinet/maven-latex-plugin/